вҠў tokenize в–ё crystallized
  given text вүЎ "hello world"
  yield tokens[]

  вҠў= tokens вҶҗ split(В«textВ», " ")

  вҠЁ tokens is a list of strings

вҠў count
  given tokenizeвҶ’tokens
  yield n

  вҲҙ Count the elements in В«tokenizeвҶ’tokensВ».

  вҠЁ n = len(В«tokenizeвҶ’tokensВ»)

вҠў describe
  given tokenizeвҶ’tokens
  given countвҶ’n
  yield summary

  вҲҙ Write a one-sentence summary: "Found В«countвҶ’nВ» tokens: В«tokenizeвҶ’tokensВ»."

  вҠЁ summary contains str(В«countвҶ’nВ»)
  вҠЁ summary is one sentence

вҖ•вҖ•вҖ•вҖ•вҖ•вҖ•вҖ•вҖ•вҖ•вҖ•вҖ•вҖ•вҖ•вҖ•вҖ•вҖ•вҖ•вҖ•вҖ•вҖ•вҖ•вҖ•вҖ•вҖ•вҖ•вҖ•вҖ•вҖ•вҖ•вҖ•вҖ•
eval-one step 0 вҶ’ step 1:
  Ready cells: [tokenize] (textвүЎ"hello world" is bound, cell is crystallized)
  Execute: tokenize (вҠў= вҖ” no LLM needed)
  Result: tokens вүЎ ["hello", "world"]
  Cost: 0 tokens (deterministic)
  Hash: h0 вҶ’ h1

eval-one step 1 вҶ’ step 2:
  Ready cells: [count] (tokenizeвҶ’tokensвүЎ["hello","world"] is bound)
  Execute: count (вҲҙ вҖ” LLM call)
  Result: n вүЎ 2
  Cost: ~50 tokens
  Hash: h1 вҶ’ h2

eval-one step 2 вҶ’ step 3:
  Ready cells: [describe] (tokenizeвҶ’tokens and countвҶ’n both bound)
  Execute: describe (вҲҙ вҖ” LLM call)
  Result: summary вүЎ "Found 2 tokens: hello, world."
  Cost: ~100 tokens
  Hash: h2 вҶ’ h3

is-done: all yields bound вҶ’ done вүЎ true
Total LLM cost: ~150 tokens (tokenize was free)
